          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怕什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怕的是拉稀跑肚。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一蹬儿，两蹬儿，上头挂着红杏儿。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一耗子，上灯台，偷油吃，下不来。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "南通州，北通州，南北通州通南北。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "东当铺，西当铺，东西当铺当东西。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大大王、刘飞虎。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二大王、江老鼠。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "请了！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你我弟兄霸占青峰岭，倒也逍遥自在。只是山寨缺少粮草，这便如何是好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这有何难！且命喽啰们下山，拔他们几根烟袋拿上山来，也够你我弟兄使用。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哎呀贤弟，你好大才小用！想当初抽旱烟使的是白铜锅、虎皮杆、翡翠嘴，拿"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "上山来，也够你我使用。如今抽的是洋烟卷，每人手里拿着根火燎杆，拿上山"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来，怎够你我弟兄使用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且听探马一报。"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "报！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐凤英讨战！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎、江老鼠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "再探！"
        },
        {
          "character": "报子",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（报子下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不好了！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（扑灯蛾） 心中乱如麻，乱如麻。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江老鼠 （扑灯蛾） 两腿弹琵琶，弹琵琶。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘飞虎 （扑灯蛾） 人说凤英武艺好，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江老鼠 （扑灯蛾） 哪个男儿胜似她！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘飞虎 （扑灯蛾） 今日下山与她战，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江老鼠 （扑灯蛾） 明日下山与她杀。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘飞虎 （扑灯蛾） 战战战！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江老鼠 （扑灯蛾） 杀杀杀！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "刘飞虎 （扑灯蛾） 杀她不过，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "江老鼠 （扑灯蛾） 我趴在地下认干妈。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦，愣叫她打死，别叫她麻死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们跟她嘎啦嘎啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎、江老鼠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "来呀！带我的走狗！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四喽兵",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四女兵、徐凤英同上，会阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！二贼通名受死！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "大大王刘飞虎！"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二大王江老鼠！"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎、江老鼠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你怕我不怕？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "尔等将山寨献出，如若不然，刀下做鬼！"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你跟她嘎啦嘎啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（江老鼠下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "徐凤英啊徐凤英！我看你年纪小，脚儿好，我劝你下得马来，跟我拜了天地，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你看好也不好？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "一派胡言！放马过来！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐凤英、刘飞虎同起打。刘飞虎、四喽兵同败下，徐凤英、四女兵同追下。）"
        }
      ],
