    {
      "scene_index": 4,
      "label": "第四场",
      "characters_present": [
        "刘飞虎",
        "徐凤英",
        "江老鼠"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘飞虎、江老鼠自两边分上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦！你把水都闹浑啦。我瞧出来啦，她要咱们的青峰岭，你有主意没有？"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我是一点主意也没有。这可怎么好哇？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我倒是有主意。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你有什么主意？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你蹲下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "蹲下干嘛？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我骑着你。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你别挨骂啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "干脆！咱们把青峰岭让给她就结啦。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "就这么一说，就让给她？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "让给她！"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "让给她？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "让给她。不让给她怎么办？"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "让给她就让给她吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我给她前面引路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我给她牵马坠镫。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "内白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "哪里走！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐凤英、四女兵同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "二贼还不将山寨献出？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎、江老鼠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦！拿您这么个人，干嘛跟我们俩嘎杂子一般见识。您的来意，我们明白啦，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎、江老鼠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "情愿将青峰岭，奉送您啦！"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我给您哪牵马，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我给您哪引路。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "如此带路上山！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
