          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四喽兵、刘飞虎、江老鼠引四女兵、徐凤英同上。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎、江老鼠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "咱们见见新寨主。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘飞虎、江老鼠同向徐凤英。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎、江老鼠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "参见新寨主！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你二人有何本领？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我们哥俩，一点能力也没有。我就会放屁。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我就会尿炕。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "仓库有何钱粮？快快献出！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘飞虎、江老鼠同背供。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎、江老鼠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有的，狼到咱们哥儿俩这儿啦，那咱们跟她说去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘飞虎、江老鼠同向徐凤英。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎、江老鼠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "我告诉您说：我们哥儿俩一个大也没有。我们要是有，不在您身上花，那算我"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎、江老鼠",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "们哥儿俩不会花，我们哥儿俩连饭落子也还没哪。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这有何难！这有令旗一面，去到湖北田虎帐下，必然收留你等，去吧！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（徐凤英付令旗。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "你瞧这个。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "念什么？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个念“今日准演”的“今”。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "这个念“全体大会”的“会”。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "得啦！别胡说啦，这个念“令”。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "念“令”？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "念“令”。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "有什么用？"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "用处大啦。咱们进了饭馆，什么好吃，咱们要什么吃；什么好喝，咱们要什么"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "喝；一吃一喝，吃的酒足饭饱，咱们拿起这个来，就这么一晃，一个大不给，"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "站起一走。"
        },
        {
          "character": "江老鼠",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不用说，人家臭奏一通。"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘飞虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "嘿嘿！人家扒衣裳。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（江老鼠、刘飞虎同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众女兵，两厢搜来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四女兵",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四女兵同搜。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "四女兵",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "四下皆空。"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "掩门！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众人同下。）"
        }
      ],
