    {
      "scene_index": 8,
      "label": "第八场",
      "characters_present": [
        "四上手",
        "四女兵",
        "徐凤英",
        "李虎"
      ],
      "lines": [
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四女兵、徐凤英同上，四上手、李虎同上，会阵。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "呔！留下车辆，放你过去！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "要俺车辆却也不难，通尔的名来！"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听者！俺乃湖北田虎帐下徐凤英是也。来将留名。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "听者！俺乃蔡相帐下旗牌官李虎。尔有何本领，擅敢前来劫夺？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "若无本领，焉敢前来劫夺？"
        },
        {
          "character": "徐凤英",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "众女兵，一齐动手！"
        },
        {
          "character": "李虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且慢！看此地窄小，这跑，跑不开爷的马；这耍，耍不开爷的鞭。找一宽阔之"
        },
        {
          "character": "李虎",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "地，见个高下。"
        },
        {
          "character": "李虎、徐凤英",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众将官）（众女兵），荒郊去者！"
        },
        {
          "character": "四上手、四女兵",
          "line_type": "同白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊！"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（四女兵、徐凤英、四上手、李虎同下。）"
        }
      ],
